### Task: Find the latest press release

#### Ideal Flow (5 Steps)
1. Land on homepage → see “Press Releases” in top navbar.
2. Click “Press Releases” → list appears, sorted newest first.
3. Find latest headline/date clearly visible.
4. Click "View Press Release →" → full article opens.

#### Friction Points in Current Page
- Lack of hover/focus feedback on links/buttons.

#### Fixes Applied
- Moved Press link to top navbar.
- Added publication date.
- Changed button text to “View Press Release →”.
- Styled hover/focus states for links and buttons.
